<p xmlns:data="http://www.w3.org/TR/html5/dom.html#custom-data-attribute" id="fs-id1170572306426"><m>\displaystyle{\int_{0}^{1} (1-6x+12x^2-8x^3)dx} =(x-3x^2+4x^3-2x^4)=(1-3+4-2)(0-0+0-0)=0</m></p></solution>


